org.batfish.datamodel.acl

Class AclTracer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.acl.Evaluator
      • org.batfish.datamodel.acl.AclTracer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericAclLineMatchExprVisitor<java.lang.Boolean>

    public final class AclTracer
extends Evaluator
    Tracer for IpAccessList, IpSpace, HeaderSpace.
    Acts like Evaluator on IpAccessList, except that it introduces tracing when encountering traceable classes.
